<body>
    <h1>20260416 - Lapu-Lapu GOCC and Japan</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"a7b3c1b16d7e" id=3D"id-20260416-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJap=
an-ApplicationMonitoringOnboarding&amp;DashboardReview=E2=80=93MeetingNotes=
">Application Monitoring Onboarding &amp; Dashboard Review =E2=80=93 Meetin=
g Notes</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ab4e4fb8021d"></p>
<p local-id=3D"b3d40f75806c"><strong><u>Implementation Plan</u></strong></p=
>
<p local-id=3D"6e5bfd8916b7"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://one=
.newrelic.com/dashboards/detail/MTczNzcwNXxWSVp8REFTSEJPQVJEfGRhOjEyMDUxOTg=
y?account=3D1737705&amp;state=3D95432be6-14bc-fb31-5335-6225a8c7d447" rel=
=3D"nofollow">GOCC &lt; New Relic</a> - GOCC Japan Application Dashboard wi=
th synthetic, APM and metrics</p>
<p local-id=3D"d0fb5458ee43">Prod - Employee Experience Dashboard (+Int=E2=
=80=99l sites)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8c91af877890">
<li local-id=3D"4a02a1a90860">
<p local-id=3D"61517e5129f2">66/88 Japan Application Systems complete</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dc95b90c978e">
<li local-id=3D"803cf5dc24b2">
<p local-id=3D"215b183eeda1">Confirm alerting/incident workflows</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fec7db727a7">
<p local-id=3D"7b41a001bd20">Rapid Recovery plans are drafted</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fdd5dbc8bef3">Non-Prod - Developer Experience Dashboard</p>
<ul local-id=3D"20a8e8746464">
<li local-id=3D"c499b4cdbc57">
<p local-id=3D"8dfa48c3718b">45/60 Groups of App Environments</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ff368b82029">
<li local-id=3D"251c1bb3-34fc-48dd-89f8-a309d1faac1e">
<p local-id=3D"5fdb7443475f">Confirm alerting/incident workflows</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"76a83110-d472-4a78-a0ff-a6b2095ffa73">
<p local-id=3D"10ff46d4ed73">APM/metrics based monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3b058afd-f8fe-4eea-8176-24cb43cba99a">
<p local-id=3D"6f8518a773ce">Rapid Recovery plans are drafted</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8043234373e5">Transition App Monitoring and BAU Operations t=
o GOCC</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e8767fd65eca">
<li local-id=3D"6596ac3b9314">
<p local-id=3D"6b36084452c7">16/65 - 9 Apps are in-progress ETA end of mont=
h (include in weekly report)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ce77caa69974">Business Capability Dashboard</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6fb12f438f30">
<li local-id=3D"1cf52cd40ee3">
<p local-id=3D"2112faa6ad26">Submit to Leadership review (Hari, Kelvin, Bir=
ger) and next steps</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a9c7c3ee948e"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"472b493df977" id=3D"id-20260416-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJapan-1.Lap=
topMonitoring">1. Laptop Monitoring</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ee23f69a-2215-4916-8b29-4e8548fcda85">
<li local-id=3D"6c579bd0-b1d1-41c6-8f5c-058f00d71664">
<p local-id=3D"b25ccfc94e53">Branch network monitoring laptops have been in=
stalled</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7da53fe9fc1a">
<li local-id=3D"86bfb1ab60df">
<p local-id=3D"379531d3717b">5 Prod: Next step is to coordinate with GOCC t=
o produce cool metrics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5601ecda858b">
<p local-id=3D"c186421a008c">2 Test: Status TBC</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5347fdb55097"></p>
<hr local-id=3D"41ced776-10d2-4419-a4c3-4b1c60ad52de">
<h2 local-id=3D"2797abf4938a" id=3D"id-20260416-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJapan-INFOR=
MED">INFORMED</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"71492de0-ca53-462e-bab0-a7e6b02292a9">
<li local-id=3D"19c3fe78-cf82-4c9e-8e9e-9e56714b8f4f">
<p local-id=3D"72fd72bfc0eb"><strong>GOCC Transition Status</strong><br>
Application monitoring transition from PS to GOCC is underway. 16 applicati=
ons are fully transitioned and 9 are in progress, against a total scope of =
65. Completion remains targeted for end of month, with known impact from Ja=
pan holidays.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15ef322d-96cf-4600-9421-c144adb7e24b">
<p local-id=3D"8bae046ccaa1"><strong>Monitoring Enablement State</strong></=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"32add906-eed4-40e4-9b8b-0af979463f5a">
<li local-id=3D"6e240878-c4e4-4441-9c7c-1da0b271675e">
<p local-id=3D"9605a29ed504">Production employee experience dashboards are =
near=E2=80=91complete.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05bbfc5b-5c8d-48d3-bf8f-bbcaae5552c7">
<p local-id=3D"d80499735b60">Non=E2=80=91production developer dashboards re=
main incomplete and require follow=E2=80=91through.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0f09f04-9867-4783-b7c7-a2dfb392f627">
<p local-id=3D"29c90512661e">Branch=E2=80=91based synthetic monitoring is l=
ive in Izumi, Osaka, and Hatsudai and generating latency data.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1e51869-e227-4fba-8ada-bead73c59b84">
<p local-id=3D"f6c7795f0a96"><strong>Risk Signals Identified</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"cc4af65e-1bdf-4dde-8907-707ecdd0a117">
<li local-id=3D"a64e0f9d-ad6c-4da4-95be-b3b10b0e76e6">
<p local-id=3D"1b5a70222b43">Workload status in New Relic can remain red du=
e to host=E2=80=91level alerts even when applications are healthy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"339573c2-1a7d-4cd4-a8e3-81ee5183ad0d">
<p local-id=3D"6211859a2581">Multiple non=E2=80=91production URLs are retur=
ning HTTP 500 errors and require application=E2=80=91team validation.</p></=
li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1ce320a2-77e0-43ab-b6d5-f5a594c5c7ce">
<h2 local-id=3D"5042307138d0" id=3D"id-20260416-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJapan-ACCEP=
TED">ACCEPTED</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"65e85a3c-10f1-470a-b336-57e17883617c">
<li local-id=3D"70ee44f4-dfa4-48e4-a431-104f52a18b6b">
<p local-id=3D"da5d57766f8a"><strong>Parallel Monitoring Model</strong><br>
PS will continue parallel monitoring for a limited post=E2=80=91go=E2=80=91=
live period to de=E2=80=91risk transition while GOCC ramps to full ownershi=
p.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"56d86789-88b1-449b-982b-5a2ee3e6393e">
<p local-id=3D"14092518e295"><strong>Single Source of Truth for Transition<=
/strong><br>
The Phase=E2=80=911 checklist file is accepted as the authoritative tracker=
 for PS =E2=86=92 GOCC handover status and will be used for weekly reportin=
g.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2aa93710-5700-4e27-8a15-3223ae2fa70b">
<p local-id=3D"a6ec75c20ddf"><strong>Alerting Philosophy</strong><br>
Alerting policies must prioritize customer and application impact; host=E2=
=80=91level noise must not drive false incidents.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"355a1407-c2b4-4ced-95d3-a1acfe67beab">
<p local-id=3D"b8cd61219656"><strong>Rapid Recovery Enablement</strong><br>
A bilingual information=E2=80=91sharing session with Japan Production Suppo=
rt is required to align on rapid recovery responsibilities and information =
flow.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e44ec3b4-e0b6-480d-99a6-97bf29376339">
<h2 local-id=3D"103b8c7e7438" id=3D"id-20260416-Lapu-LapuGOCCandJapan-DECID=
ED">DECIDED</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a68ed444-cc13-42a3-ad1c-4fe4e741b78d">
<li local-id=3D"ecfce816-e8c6-4fca-ad30-a48dbbf8d3b4">
<p local-id=3D"593cc2ea5cfb"><strong>Tracking &amp; Reporting</strong><br>
The weekly report will explicitly list each application transitioned to GOC=
C, sourced from the handover checklist.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f4b2e96-82da-4eaa-9cf7-4790d7a84e35">
<p local-id=3D"31ecee46564d"><strong>Ownership =E2=80=94 Monitoring Configu=
ration</strong><br>
The Observability team will define and implement audit=E2=80=91compliant be=
st practices for credentials used in synthetic monitoring and customer jour=
ney checks.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7bd6e40d-c7e8-4015-8ed0-928871c1382c">
<p local-id=3D"8b5f184c5a0e"><strong>Workload Status Policy</strong><br>
A new workload=E2=80=91status rule will be created to prevent non=E2=80=91i=
mpactful host alerts from marking workloads as unhealthy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"188f5912-d782-4b84-bd21-aaaa5e01f0d6">
<p local-id=3D"4be638c2d03c"><strong>Error Resolution Path</strong><br>
Non=E2=80=91production 500 errors will be consolidated, documented with evi=
dence, and escalated to the respective application teams for resolution.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"620f1b2e-5e04-450d-a504-535d48b68dbf">
<p local-id=3D"700810234c74"><strong>Rapid Recovery Session Execution</stro=
ng><br>
A 90=E2=80=91minute bilingual session will be executed (75 mins content / 1=
5 mins Q&amp;A) using Ingenium as the reference implementation, with materi=
als shared in advance.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b7b51c6b-90b4-4c73-9f19-8aa76a1b7999">
